- Bible (read first): `EUSOTRIP2027GOLD/00_THE_BIBLE.md`
- Brand + design tokens: `EUSOTRIP2027GOLD/01_Brand_DNA_and_Design_Rules.md`
- Engineering principles (TDD, E2E): `EUSOTRIP2027GOLD/02_Engineering_Principles.md`
- Backend API contract: `EUSOTRIP2027GOLD/03_Backend_API_Contract.md`
- DB schema: `EUSOTRIP2027GOLD/04_Database_and_Schema.md`
- Auth/Security: `EUSOTRIP2027GOLD/05_Auth_Security_Compliance.md`
- Integrations (HERE, Stripe, Plaid, APNs): `EUSOTRIP2027GOLD/06_Third_Party_Integrations.md`
- Role doctrine: `EUSOTRIP2027GOLD/10_Mode_TRUCK/`, `20_Mode_RAIL/`, `30_Mode_VESSEL/`
- Journeys + lifecycle: `EUSOTRIP2027GOLD/80_User_Journeys_and_Load_Lifecycle.md`
- Claude Code init: `EUSOTRIP2027GOLD/95_Codebase_Continuity_and_Claude_Init.md`
