- Shipped bricks (ledger): `EUSOTRIP2027GOLD/autorun_ledger/`

## When in doubt

Ask: "which file in `EUSOTRIP2027GOLD/` governs this?" If you cannot find one, the change is probably outside the doctrine — flag it in PR description and add a doctrine entry in the same PR.

**EusoTrip 2027 — Taking our talents on the road. Driver is home base; every role extends it.**
